  "description": "<p>· <em><strong>Attractive remuneration and career growth</strong></em></p><p>·<em><strong>Commission + AWS+ Variable Bonus</strong></em></p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>·Build and manage customer relationships to drive sales growth</p><p>·Attend to enquiries, gather feedback, and maintain customer records</p><p>· leads and expand the customer base</p><p>· through regular visits, food fairs, trade shows, and events</p><p>·Work with R&D on product improvements based on market feedback</p><p>·Follow up on orders, deliveries, and outstanding payments</p><p>·Conduct basic market research and support marketing activities<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·Min. Diploma or equivalent.</p><p>·Familiar with food products, industry trends, and basic product advice</p><p>· Valid driving license is an advantage<br /></p><p><strong>WORKING AREA - ISLAND WIDE -(NOT WFH)</strong><br /></p><p>TALENT LINK SOLUTION – (23C1962)</p><p>PATRICK POH</p><p>Reg No - R1107847</p><p>WhatsApp- +659108969</p>",
